di ungerishe, hobn zey ale genumen tsam

00:16:48.057 --> 00:16:49.856
un m'hot zey gefirt oyf Poyln.

00:16:51.229 --> 00:16:52.792
du host dos gezen?

00:16:52.393 --> 00:16:53.180
yo.

00:16:53.592 --> 00:16:54.429
mayn

