00:17:11.782 --> 00:17:14.254
dos iz geven erev tishebov in

00:17:13.930 --> 00:17:15.245
eyn un fertsiker yor.

00:17:14.879 --> 00:17:16.218
eyn un fertsik.

00:17:16.238 --> 00:17:18.476
un nokh dem vos hot pasirt?

