00:18:11.115 --> 00:18:13.017
nor di tsvey brider zenen gevezn.

00:18:13.017 --> 00:18:15.176
yo, un dernokh dem, ikh ⟨hob⟩ fargesn tsu zogn

00:18:15.199 --> 00:18:18.503
undzere briders hobn di ungern genumen

00:18:18.503 --> 00:18:21.001
in di armey, nor nisht in di armey

00:18:21.001 --> 00:18:22.601
nor arbets lager.

