ale tsu fus zenen mir avekgan fuftsn ober tsvontsik kilometer.

00:21:05.046 --> 00:21:06.795
di mame iz geforn oyf a vogn

00:21:07.122 --> 00:21:08.330
in geto arayn.

00:21:08.303 --> 00:21:10.356
un di andere yidn fun ZHUKOVO?

00:21:10.076 --> 00:21:10.966
oykh azoy.

00:21:11.053 --> 00:21:12.852
d- ale in eynem zenen mir gegan.

00:21:14.040 --> 00:21:15.958
un on shikh

