dort zenen mir geven fir vokhn, biz eyn un tsvontsikstn

00:22:11.719 --> 00:22:13.008
may.

00:22:12.934 --> 00:22:18.947
un voser, voser shtub hos- hot dos geven dortn in MUKACHEVO, in der geto?

